SMITH, Respondent, v. RENTZ, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. February 16, 1894.) Action by Eugene Smith, as executor, etc., against Fredericka Rentz.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and O’BRIEN and FOLLETT, JJ.

Leopold Leo, for appellant. H. B- Olosson, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs. See 26 N. Y. Supp. 1115.
